{"tid":1856425,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"罷工係時代革命一部分，你知道嗎？","createTime":"2020-02-01T15:13:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T15:29:34.000Z","uid":126621,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"95d1f3c19a40a7169ff5800f289ea83bc67cdb26","tid":1856425,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T15:13:56.000Z","msg":"1.<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">醫護界資源比狗隊少</span></strong><br />\nblue object <span style=\"color: red;\">24,110元 至 38,580元 </span><br />\nwhite object <span style=\"color: gold;\">45,305元 至 84,250元</span> <br />\n<br />\n三B級病人服務助理<span style=\"color: red;\">11,866元至14,064元</span><br />\n一級病人服務助理<span style=\"color: red;\">21,389元至25,199元</span><br />\n現時醫管局約有25,000名病人服務助理、運作助理及行政助理。<br />\n<br />\nEN <span style=\"color: red;\">20,610 至 43,783</span><br />\nRN <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">32,675 至 52,578</span></span><br />\n<br />\n2.<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">仇恨</span></strong><br />\n大半年打壓知識份子<br />\n當中不少醫護人士被打拉射告<br />\n而家就有事求人<br />\n<br />\n3.<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">無保障</span></strong><br />\n封關只係其中一樣<br />\n大劣病人根本唔守規矩<br />\n人地支那都識立法保護醫護人員<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200130/mobile/bkn-20200130111932894-0130_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20200130%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200130111932894-0130_00952_001.html&d=ANzGKs6Ysw%2B%2BKy1wioRXt0lZDiKRLpOq3%2FNqhGVOPOo%3D&h=4e3a0a57\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200130/mobile/bkn-20200130111932894-0130_00952_001.html</a><br />\n而且不幸染病死左只有50萬賠償真係on9<br />\n夠你供樓養父母老婆仔女？300萬都唔夠啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">對應解決方法</span></span><br />\n1.cut 狗隊資源及一半人工<br />\n提升醫護界薪金2倍<br />\n<br />\n2.答應五大訴求，追究警暴，放義士，<br />\n高官問責，實行雙普選，減仇恨<br />\n<br />\n3.提升醫護個人裝備，立法限制病人行為<br />\n立即全面封關，賠償額提升到500萬<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">根本你做少一樣，醫護都唔會開工</span></span>"},{"pid":"4e0d1873661d185a6205dbc022571076cddc754d","tid":1856425,"uid":126621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T15:15:22.000Z","msg":"5 demands , not one less"},{"pid":"1aa6da7f0285d154912660b5f69e95fe7e87dad9","tid":1856425,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T15:17:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f22b3106513f0a0b32ba01bb2d43900e8f5a29eb","tid":1856425,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T15:20:09.000Z","msg":"「罷工」港龍員工需要支持！請幫忙宣傳！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1856363\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1856363</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"eb77f170d521331dca73563deb7d4b56767d4ef0","tid":1856425,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T15:23:48.000Z","msg":"啱呀<br />\n大家有眼睇<br />\n連最基本都唔做<br />\n奶共奶到癲撚咗"},{"pid":"60bf4bb783d04d7b77fc3c59765a1b0eb150db9a","tid":1856425,"uid":30115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T15:24:32.000Z","msg":"力推"},{"pid":"3c9cfccb509d11182606f8983206734f1e2d9d68","tid":1856425,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T15:29:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}